<h2 id="using-hero">Using hero</h2>

<p>A hero image is used to promote council campaigns.</p>

<p>Images should always:</p>
<ul>
  <li>be meaningful and support the campaign</li>
  <li>be text-free - text should be added to the <a href="overlay">overlay</a>, not the image</li>
  <li>have alt text</li>
</ul>

<p>A hero image can be used on the homepage and landing pages that have a campaign focus, such as the news landing page.</p>

<p>It shouldnâ€™t be used on information and topic pages.</p>
